\begin_layout Subsection
Biais à la perte
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Among those who should have updated, those who revised their subjective
 gain upwards were disproportionately correct in doing so than those whose
 revised it downards, indicating a bias towards loss when updating.
\end_layout

